import React from 'react'
import { Divider, Toolbar, Typography, Box, Grid, Paper, Link } from '@mui/material'
import { makeStyles } from '@mui/styles'

// Styles for the page components
const useStyles = makeStyles((theme) => ({
  title: {
    fontWeight: 'bold',
    color: '#3f51b5',
  },
  featureBox: {
    borderRadius: '10px',
    boxShadow: '0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)',
    padding: theme.spacing(4),
    textAlign: 'center',
    backgroundColor: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7)', // Transparent background
    transition: 'transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease',
    '&:hover': {
      transform: 'translateY(-10px)',
      boxShadow: '0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3)',
    },
  },
  footer: {
    backgroundColor: '#3f51b5',
    color: 'white',
    padding: theme.spacing(4),
    marginTop: theme.spacing(4),
    borderRadius: '10px',
    boxShadow: '0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)',
  },
  footerColumn: {
    display: 'flex',
    flexDirection: 'column',
    alignItems: 'center',
  },
  footerTitle: {
    fontWeight: 'bold',
    marginBottom: theme.spacing(1),
  },
  footerLink: {
    color: 'white',
    textDecoration: 'none',
    marginTop: theme.spacing(1),
  },
}))

export default function Home() {
  const classes = useStyles()

  return (
    <>
      <Toolbar>
        <Typography variant='h6' className={classes.title}>Features of My Bank</Typography>
      </Toolbar>
      <Divider />

      {/* Feature Boxes Section */}
      <Box sx={{ padding: 4, display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-around' }}>
        <Grid container spacing={3} justifyContent="center">
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
            <Paper className={classes.featureBox}>
              <Typography variant="h6">Easy Transactions</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2">Make seamless transfers and manage your bank accounts with ease.</Typography>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
            <Paper className={classes.featureBox}>
              <Typography variant="h6">24/7 Support</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2">Our customer support team is available around the clock to assist you.</Typography>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
            <Paper className={classes.featureBox}>
              <Typography variant="h6">Secure Banking</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2">Your account security is our priority, with top-notch encryption.</Typography>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Box>

      {/* Footer Section */}
      <Box className={classes.footer}>
        <Grid container spacing={3}>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} className={classes.footerColumn}>
            <Typography variant="h6" className={classes.footerTitle}>About</Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2">Learn more about our history, mission, and values.</Typography>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} className={classes.footerColumn}>
            <Typography variant="h6" className={classes.footerTitle}>Contact</Typography>
            <Link href="mailto:support@mybank.com" className={classes.footerLink}>Email Us</Link>
            <Link href="tel:+123456789" className={classes.footerLink}>Call Us</Link>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Box>
    </>
  )
}
